      "title": "New bus fares to be announced today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The interim bus fare revision after the recent fuel price increase, will be announced today, the National Transport Commission (NTC) said.",
        "The annual bus fare revision is announced on July 1 every year.",
        "Following a discussion on Tuesday (28), it was decided to raise bus fares by 30% while increasing the minimum fare to Rs.40 which is currently at Rs.32.",
        "The discussion held at the Ministry between Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardana, the National Transport Commission (NTC), Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) and private bus owners. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
